1	//! Goal2 binary: two actors, each on its own thread, ping-ponging
2	//! an empty [`Message`] over `std::sync::mpsc` channels for a
3	//! caller-supplied duration in seconds, after an optional warmup.
4	//! Prints messages-handled / throughput, an apparatus-overhead
5	//! diagnostic, and a `tprobe` band-table report per actor.
6	//!
7	//! Unlike goal1, `inner` is fixed at 1: ping-pong keeps at most
8	//! one message in flight per channel, so batched probe scopes
9	//! could never fill. If we later add a workload with deeper
10	//! per-channel queues we'll revisit.
11	//!
12	//! Usage: `goal2 --help`
